# Module 6 â€“ Nexus Repository + Gradle (Artifact Management)

## Overview
This module documents the complete step-by-step process of setting up Sonatype Nexus Repository and publishing a Gradle-built Java artifact.

## Step-by-Step Process

### SSH into Server
```bash
ssh -i ~/.ssh/id_ed25519 root@<SERVER_PUBLIC_IP>
```

### Update Server
```bash
apt update -y && apt upgrade -y
```

### Install Java
```bash
apt install -y openjdk-17-jdk
java -version
```

### Install Gradle
```bash
apt install -y gradle
gradle -v
```

### Create Gradle Project
```bash
mkdir -p ~/gradle-nexus-demo
cd ~/gradle-nexus-demo
gradle init
gradle build
```

### Configure build.gradle
```gradle
plugins {
    id 'java'
    id 'maven-publish'
}

group = 'com.demo'
version = '1.0.0'
```

### Publish Artifact
```bash
gradle clean build publish
```

### Verify in Nexus UI
Navigate to maven-releases and confirm artifact upload.

## Status
Completed